      <title>黎巴嫩名称前HSBC银行家Souaid为中央银行州长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/lebanon-names-ex-hsbc-banker-souaid-as-central-bank-governor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黎巴嫩名为Karim Souaid为中央银行州长，选择了一位私营部门的财务专家，领导了长期以来的经济大修，以遭受多年危机和最近与以色列战争的袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/lebanon-names-ex-hsbc-banker-souaid-as-central-bank-governor</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 14:41:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
